{"tid":1086481,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"新BMW M135i將會與新1 series共同有重大改變","createTime":"2019-03-31T20:07:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-23T04:52:09.000Z","uid":236926,"like":2,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"91c666d263af45752a61957e9ec1803f5a7527fb","tid":1086481,"uid":236926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T20:07:33.000Z","msg":"之前已確認新1系將會與Mini共用前驅底盤<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NtxHkW5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNtxHkW5.jpg&h=1905813a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但而家又另外確定，到時候Top of the range的車款將會用－副新研發的2.0 4氣缸 Turbo引擎，馬力會有302匹<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XAVBqoQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXAVBqoQ.jpg&h=7f482514&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而新的M135i，因新底盤的關係，六氣缸引擎將不會有足夠空間容納。所以將會用&quot;a newly-developed lump based on an existing 2.0-litre turbocharged block. with reinforced crank and con-rods, a larger turbo and new injector valves&quot;，指望能加強輸出及保持同級內的競爭力<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M09behg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM09behg.jpg&h=2fe7b81b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n馬力數字上預計將會比現行款的M140i少30匹。但會標準配置xDrive四驅系統。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vAOO0Xo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvAOO0Xo.jpg&h=88fd12ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外為左改善由後驅轉前驅在操控上帶來的影響，新車將會從i3技術移植ECU內置的&quot;slip-limiting tech&quot;，防止嚴重的「推頭」情況。及有－項&quot;Brake-based Torque vectoring&quot;功能為標準配備，有需要時彎內的前輪會自己減速以助收緊行車線"},{"pid":"6c6ca4c98e35fc02bcb13db4e4a51cdc4c0fd615","tid":1086481,"uid":196924,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T22:48:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你換mini底盤都算，變埋直四真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b71bd09ba7c769fc35dbe8b3c30ec675395369ec","tid":10